Return _the **maximum** number of enemy forts that can be captured_. In case it is **impossible** to move your army, or you do not have any fort under your command, return `0`_._ Since 4 is the maximum number of enemy forts that can be captured, we return 4. **Explanation:** Since no enemy fort can be captured, 0 is returned.
